        <img src="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evidence_Action#/media/File:Evidence-action-vectorized.svg" alt="Evidence Action Banner">
        <h1>Welcome to Evidence Action</h1>
        <p>Evidence Action is a non-profit organization that scales proven interventions to improve the lives of millions. Our work focuses on two key areas: **nutrition** and **safe water**.</p>
        <h2>Our Focus Areas</h2>
        <h3>Nutrition</h3>
        <p>We work to deliver evidence-based nutrition programs, such as deworming for school-aged children, to improve health and educational outcomes. By targeting neglected diseases, we help ensure children can attend school and learn effectively.</p>
        <h3>Safe Water</h3>
        <p>Our safe water programs, like our dispenser-based chlorination initiatives, provide clean drinking water to communities. This simple, cost-effective solution prevents waterborne diseases and saves lives.</p>
        <p>To learn more, visit our official website.</p>
